15:34.320 --> 15:35.000
It's a lot of fun.

15:38.660 --> 15:41.360
There have been complaints, but they don't get farther with them.

15:43.500 --> 15:46.080
I solve the problem with complaints.

15:46.280 --> 15:48.080
